            <div class="LowerTitle">I’m still confused about “cold pressed” versus traditional juicing processes. Can you explain more?</div></br>
                Traditional (centrifugal) juicing processes involve extensive friction (heat), which destroys the enzymes and nutrients within the fruits and vegetables.
                </br>
